description: This header file defines the interface and exports for the SNMP plugin in the Advanced Networking Service Container. It includes function declarations for initialization, support checks, unloading, and memory management related to the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the SNMP plugin with the maximum supported version and plugin information.

methods.name: COSA_Async_Init
methods.description: Performs asynchronous initialization of the SNMP plugin.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjectSupported
methods.description: Checks if a specific object is supported by the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Unloads the plugin, performing necessary cleanup.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryCheck
methods.description: Performs a check of memory usage related to the plugin.
